                    SF-ADJUSTMENT _"Number of first frame" '(18 0 36 1 3 0 1)
                    SF-ADJUSTMENT _"Sprocketholes till first frame" '(1 1 8 1 3 0 1)
                    SF-ADJUSTMENT _"First hole after x mm" '(1 -2.5 2.5 0.5 1 1 1)
